{
  "stem": "7506.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had to leave her studies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She did that, and before she got married to my father, lived in Holland, and was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my mother did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think we lived rent-free in that apartment, [PAUSES] supplied by the city hall of Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I didn't know what I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES] Jopi's parents, his father, suggested would I like to become a silversmith, [PAUSES] which is very particular in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I-- so he took me to a friend of his.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, this man will give you an apprenticeship free.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Those days, to be an apprentice, you had to pay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES] So after I met the man and I went to his-- we call it in Dutch, like the French, it was 'atelier.' [PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't that interested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Jopi's father-- I used to call him [INAUDIBLE], which is a shortening from-- for [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jacobus. ?] [PAUSES] He said, would you like to learn the diamond business from the very bottom up?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what your father was in, your grandfather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why don't you do that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, I don't know if I want to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, well, he said, maybe I could, through this silversmith, get you an apprenticeship free.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES] This silversmith, with Jopi's father, went to the bourse, the diamond bourse in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And there were a few Jewish men there, diamond business, either from Belgium or that had come back-- three came back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Three or four came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they asked whether they would take me, as a survivor of a [INAUDIBLE] would teach me the business.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they agreed to take me free.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
